    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm so excited to share my absolute pride and joy with you! This car is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it seriously looks like it just rolled off the lot. It drives like a dream and has been kept sparkling clean inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Let me know if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
