      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) in Chaste White. This example retains its numbers-matching 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant, featuring a flawlessly functioning sequential turbocharger system with no boost leaks or vacuum degradation. The chassis remains structurally pristine, benefiting from the original double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen limited-slip differential that ensures surgical cornering precision. Recent compression testing confirms peak rotor health across all faces. Every factory heat shield is intact, and the five-speed manual transmission shifts with tactile, short-throw mechanical engagement. This is a zero-compromise, turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak 90s JDM performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
