    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its deep, factory-fresh luster without a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely free of creasing or wear, still carrying that distinct showroom aroma. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with all scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands perfection. Viewing is essential to appreciate the flawless craftsmanship and silent, powerful performance of this showroom-quality vehicle.",
