      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This S54-powered coupe features a meticulously maintained individual throttle body (ITB) induction system, delivering an instantaneous 8,000 RPM redline. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement using high-performance shells. The chassis has undergone professional subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with no signs of oxidation or swirl marks. The interior features Nappa leather with original factory bolsters showing zero compression. This is a mechanically synchronized, analog masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast.",
